# Host-only / editor artifacts
apps/web/.atl
Stitch

# Local dev env overrides — Vite loads .env.local during `vite build` too, not just `vite dev`.
# apps/web/.env.local sets VITE_ENABLE_MSW=true for local `npm run dev`; leaking it into the
# Docker image bakes MSW's mock service worker into the "production" bundle, which then
# intercepts every fetch (including /api/v1/auth/login) in the browser instead of hitting nginx.
**/.env.local
**/.env*.local
